    public class FeatureCollectionConverterWfs10
extends Object
implements com.thoughtworks.xstream.converters.Converter
    This class works in conjunction with XStream to convert a WfsFeatureCollection to XML according to the GML 3.2.1 spec. It will also convert respective XML into a WfsFeatureCollection.
